<s> I think you are confusing XML with particular applications of XML.  </s>
<s> Word 2000 XHTML attempts to be valid XML (I haven't checked) but is still proprietory.  </s>
<s> XML is a framework for markup languages, not a specific  </s>
<s> markup language.  </s>
<s> DOCBOOK XML is an open specification for an application of XML for technical documents, but is radically different from Word 2000 XML (it is probably not suitable for the average word processor user as it is strongly structured).  </s>
<s> Assuming Word 2000 XML is valid, both it and DOCBOOK can equally claim to be XML even though one is proprietory and I'd be surprised if Word 2000 could render DOCBOOK as anything other than the source text.  </s>
